objectives.ru:
1)	Углубить знания об истории и поэтике русской литературы второй половины XVIII – первой половины XIX века;
2)	Расширить представления о социальных факторах в истории литературы, об отношениях писателей и публики, литературы и власти, взаимодействии агентов в литературном поле;
3)	Освоить анализ культурных явлений в исторической и социальной перспективе.

objectives.en:
1) To deepen knowledge about the history and poetics of Russian literature of the second half of the 18th - first half of the 19th centuries;
2) To expand the understanding of social factors in the history of literature, the relationship between writers and the public, literature and power, the interaction of agents in the literary field;
3) To analyse of cultural phenomena in historical and social perspective.

Part 2:

) To expand students' knowledge of the modernist period of Russian literature
2) To shape and improve students' skills in analyzing a literary text. To draw their attention to the peculiarities of the structure of a symbolic text
3) To form students' idea of the symbolic creation of life and myth on which their texts are based

learning_outcomes.ru:
По окончании курса студент:
1)	Знает и умеет анализировать литературные факты в историческом контексте;
2)	Умеет анализировать социальные факторы в истории литературы, оценивать их влияние на индивидуальную поэтику;
3)	Имеет представление о русском литературном каноне, его становлении и факторах его формирования.

learning_outcomes.en:
After completing the course the student 
1) knows and can analyse literary facts in a historical context;
2) is able to analyse social factors in the history of literature and assess their impact on individual poetics;
3) has an idea of the Russian literary canon, its formation and factors of its formation.

Part 2. L.Pild

Student who has completed the second part of the course:

 -has systematic knowledge of the aesthetics and poetics of Russian symbolism;


- has an idea of the texts of Russian symbolists of the late 19th and early 20th centuries;


- can analyze the peculiarities of a Russian symbolist novel;


- can analyze the peculiarities of Russian decadent poetry;


- can work independently with literary material;


- can analyze and critically evaluate literary research related to the topic

learning_outcomes.et:
Õppeaine läbinud üliõpilane:
1) tunneb ja suudab analüüsida kirjandusloo fakte kaasaegse situatsiooni kontekstis;
2) oskab analüüsida kirjandusloo sotsiaalseid tegureid, hinnata nende mõju individuaalsele poeetikale;
3) omab ettekujutust vene kirjanduskaanonist, selle kujunemisest ja kujunemisteguritest.


Osa 2..L,Pild .Kursuse 2. osa läbinud üliõpilane:

Omab süsteemseid teadmisi vene sümbolismi esteetikast ning poeetikast;
Omab ettekujutust 19.saj lõpu- 20.saj alguse vene sümbolistide tekstidest;
Oskab välja tuua ning analüüsida vene sümbolistliku romaani erisusi;
Suudab kirjeldada ja analüüsida vene dekadentliku luule eripära;
Suudab iseseisvalt töötada allikmaterjalidega
Oskab analüüsida ja kriitiliselt hinnata teemaga seotud kirjandusteaduslikke uurimusi.
